        <content type="html" xml:base="https://markynose.github.io/blog/smart-emerge-network-aware/">&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;smart-emerge&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; is a wrapper script I use to offload Gentoo compilation to my
home server (&lt;code&gt;femboy&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;) via distcc. It worked fine as long as I was sitting on
the home LAN — but the moment I took ThiccPad somewhere else, it would just
silently fall back to local builds, which is slow.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I finally sat down and made it actually smart.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;what-it-does-now&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#what-it-does-now&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: what-it-does-now&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;What it does now&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check if we&#x27;re home&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; — looks for the home SSID (&lt;code&gt;TP-Link_F22C&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;) or an
active ethernet connection&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If on LAN&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; — use distcc directly, same as before&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If off-site&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; — bring up &lt;code&gt;wg0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; and reach &lt;code&gt;femboy&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; through the tunnel&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If the tunnel fails too&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; — prompt: build locally or abort&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On the way back&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; — if &lt;code&gt;wg0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; is up and we&#x27;re back on LAN, tear it down
automatically&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That last point matters because the new WireGuard config is full-tunnel
(&lt;code&gt;0.0.0.0&#x2F;0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;). The old one only tunneled &lt;code&gt;192.168.0.0&#x2F;24&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, so leaving it up
on LAN was harmless. Full-tunnel with wg0 up on the home network breaks
everything, so teardown has to be automatic.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;network-detection&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#network-detection&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: network-detection&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;Network detection&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;is_home_lan&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;() {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;    # check SSID (wireless)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    local&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; ssid&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;    ssid&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;iwgetid&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -r&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; 2&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    [[&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;$ssid&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; ==&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;TP-Link_F22C&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; ]] &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;    # check for active ethernet&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    for&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; iface&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; in&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; &#x2F;sys&#x2F;class&#x2F;net&#x2F;en*&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; do&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;        iface&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;basename&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;$iface&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;        local&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; state&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;        state&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;cat&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;sys&#x2F;class&#x2F;net&#x2F;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;$iface&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;operstate&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; 2&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        [[&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;$state&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; ==&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;up&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; ]] &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    done&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;wireguard-bring-up-and-teardown&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#wireguard-bring-up-and-teardown&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: wireguard-bring-up-and-teardown&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;WireGuard bring-up and teardown&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;ensure_tunnel&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;() {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    wg&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; show wg0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;   # already up&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    wg-quick&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; up wg0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; || return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;    # give it a moment to establish&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    sleep&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    ping&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -c1 -W2 10.5.5.1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;    # check femboy is reachable&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;teardown_if_home&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;() {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    wg&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; show wg0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;|| return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6272A4;&quot;&gt;   # not up, nothing to do&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    is_home_lan&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt; wg-quick&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; down wg0&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;the-main-logic&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#the-main-logic&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: the-main-logic&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;The main logic&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #F8F8F2; background-color: #282A36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;main&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;() {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    teardown_if_home&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    if&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt; is_home_lan&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; then&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;        log&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;on LAN — using distcc directly&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;        run_emerge&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB86C;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;$@&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;        return&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    fi&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;    log&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;off-site — attempting WireGuard tunnel&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    if&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt; ensure_tunnel&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; then&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;        log&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;tunnel up — using distcc via 10.5.5.2&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;        run_emerge&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB86C;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;$@&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    else&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #8BE9FD;&quot;&gt;        echo&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;distcc unreachable (LAN and tunnel both failed)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #8BE9FD;&quot;&gt;        read&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; -rp&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;build locally? [y&#x2F;N] &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt; answer&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        [[&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;$answer&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; =~&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; ^[Yy]$ ]]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt; ||&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #8BE9FD;&quot;&gt; exit&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt; 1&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #BD93F9;&quot;&gt;        MAKEOPTS&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;-j$(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt;nproc&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #F1FA8C;&quot;&gt;)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50FA7B;&quot;&gt; run_emerge&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FFB86C;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;$@&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #E9F284;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #FF79C6;&quot;&gt;    fi&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;wireguard-config-change&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#wireguard-config-change&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: wireguard-config-change&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;WireGuard config change&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The old config only routed &lt;code&gt;192.168.0.0&#x2F;24&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; through the tunnel — a split
tunnel just for reaching home network addresses. Replaced it with a
full-tunnel config (&lt;code&gt;AllowedIPs = 0.0.0.0&#x2F;0, ::&#x2F;0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;) so all traffic goes
through when I&#x27;m out, which is what I actually want.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tested the new config: came up clean, &lt;code&gt;femboy&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; reachable at &lt;code&gt;10.5.5.2&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;,
distcc handshake working. The auto-teardown on LAN detection also works —
connecting to &lt;code&gt;TP-Link_F22C&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; triggers the check and &lt;code&gt;wg-quick down wg0&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; runs
before emerge even starts.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One less thing to remember to do manually.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
